NoiseEditorController - Class in gui
FXML controller for the noiseEditor window here noisprofiles can be edited every change is persisted to the database
NoiseEditorController() - Constructor for class gui.NoiseEditorController
 
NoiseProfile - Class in persistence.model
dom-object representing a noiseprofile this object can be mapped to the database as json-entry fields: id - the path of the audio file constantNoise - name of the constantNoiseFile amplifier - int value of the noise amplifier scratches - list of scratches(dom-objects) length - number of frames that the playerThread reads until finished timesPlayed - counter of how many times the song has been played
NoiseProfile() - Constructor for class persistence.model.NoiseProfile
 
NoiseProfile(String) - Constructor for class persistence.model.NoiseProfile
 
NoiseProvider - Class in service.playback
Provides all noise-data needed while playing back audio there are two different methods used to save the data regardless of the noise-type the audiodata is split into 4096 byte frames this is the size of the buffer the PlayerThread reads audiodata from the audiofile so if noise should be added, each field of the noise and audio frame/arrays can be added and returned for the constant noise a list of frames is provided which is iterated in a loop until the song ends for the scratch noises a hashmap is provided, the key in this map are the framenumber the noise should be played at when processing the next frame, the PlayerThread always tells the NoiseProvider on which number of frame he is
NoiseProvider() - Constructor for class service.playback.NoiseProvider
 
NoiseProviderException - Exception in exceptions
custom exception thrown while loading noises in the noiseprovider
NoiseProviderException() - Constructor for exception exceptions.NoiseProviderException
 
NoiseProviderException(String) - Constructor for exception exceptions.NoiseProviderException
 
NoiseProviderException(Throwable) - Constructor for exception exceptions.NoiseProviderException
 
NoiseProviderException(String, Throwable) - Constructor for exception exceptions.NoiseProviderException
